author: Coffeezilla
description:
Investigating how much people "hate" money with a forex guru. Whistlin Diesel recently created a video called Turning $10k into $1M to prove people are lazy (Ep. 1), where he seeks to show people how easy it is to make money. We took a deep dive to learn who he's featuring, and why. 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nmszAU0UClY

I reached out for comment to both Cody and Alex which I've excerpted for the video but left in full for transparency:
